  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Which expression is equivalent to&nbsp;<math alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared plus 6 right parenthesis\"><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow><mo>(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>6</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></math>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
