      "id": "8c5c039b-9130-4199-b834-e36f585fc62e",
      "content": "<p><math alttext=\"4 x squared plus 24\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mn>4</mn>\n\t\t<msup>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t</msup>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t<mn>24</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math></p>"
    },
    {
