      "content": "<p><math alttext=\"4 x squared plus 10\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mn>4</mn>\n\t\t<msup>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t</msup>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t<mn>10</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math></p>"
