  "rationale": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is correct. The expression <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared plus 6 right parenthesis\"><mn>4</mn><mo>(</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo></math> can be rewritten as <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared right parenthesis plus 4 left parenthesis 6 right parenthesis\"><mn>4</mn><mfenced><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>(</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo></math>, which is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 x squared plus 24\"><mn>4</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>24</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect. This expression is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared plus five halves right parenthesis\"><mn>4</mn><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared plus 6 right parenthesis\"><mn>4</mn><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is incorrect. This expression is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared plus three halves right parenthesis\"><mn>4</mn><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared plus 6 right parenthesis\"><mn>4</mn><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is incorrect. This expression is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared minus one half right parenthesis\"><mn>4</mn><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"4 left parenthesis x squared plus 6 right parenthesis\"><mn>4</mn><mfenced><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>.</p>",
